													</header>
													<div class="marge">
<ul>
<li>Ringing alarm</li>
<li>Display in the tab as so to remain visible whilst navigating</li>
<li>Colorful display in green, orange and red for less than a minute, 30 seconds and 15 seconds respectively</li>
<li>Activation pomodori with a single mouse click for more than 40 pre-programmed times</li>
<li>Remove timer in one click.</li>
</ul>
